Made in 3 days for Ludum Dare 23, some parts of the code were a bit rushed, but the core of the game structure is pretty nice.
Keep in mind the game was done in Flash IDE; all graphics and sounds are in it, this is only the code.

Game at: http://www.iggyzuk.com/stuff/games/greedwars/

